    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior retains its deep, glossy finish, though a discerning eye will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and small surface scratches near the trunk latch consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with premium upholstery that shows minimal bolster wear and absolutely no tears or stains. Every feature functions exactly as intended, from the responsive touchscreen interface and dual-zone climate control to the panoramic sunroof. Mechanically, the car is in robust health; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection completed just last month. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears without hesitation. I have retained a complete folder of service receipts to provide the next owner with full peace of mind regarding its history. This is a reliable, attractive, and well-cared-for vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
